Lazygit Addon - Git repo menu v0.2

USAGE:
	Just run lg from anywhere. If you are currently in a git repo, lazygit
	will launch. If you aren't, a menu of all your git repos will appear.

REQUIRED:

1.	$GITPATH needs to be set to the directory where all of your git repos
	are saved.

	To set $GITPATH, launch lg with the '--setgitpath' option.

2.	System has to be set up to with SetupDX2




